der-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #c=
cc;"> a paper</a> finding that =E2=80=9Chedge fund managers who own powerfu=
l sports cars take on more investment risk but do not deliver higher return=
s.=E2=80=9D And now <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/clic=
k/29707590.273527/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYXBlcnMuc3Nybi5jb20vc29sMy9wYXBlcnMuY2ZtP2Fic=
